================================================================================

This software provides Model Context Protocol (MCP) server functionality
for Bear Notes application, enabling Claude AI to interact with Bear's
note database through a comprehensive set of tools for reading, writing,
and managing notes.

Key Features:
- Direct Bear database access with safety protections
- Comprehensive note search and analysis capabilities  
- Tag validation and sanitization according to Bear's requirements
- Automatic backup system for write operations
- Full-text search with relevance scoring
- Note analytics and relationship analysis

